// rule send & install example

relation r(P: Dkal.Principal)
relation ins(R: Dkal.Rule)
relation start()

---p1-----------------------------
knows start()

if start()
do
    send to p2: ins(with X: Dkal.Principal  if r(X) do send to p1: r(X))
    forget start()

---p2-----------------------------
knows r(p2)

with R: Dkal.Rule
upon p1 said ins(R)
do install R
